# Backend

```
routes ‚Üí controllers ‚Üí services ‚Üí Prisma
```

- Zod on routes, `sendSuccess`/`sendNotFound` in controllers
- Prisma only in services; orders use `$transaction` (stock + order + cart clear)
- `app.ts` exports `createApp()`; `server.ts` local dev; `api/index.ts` ‚Üí `backend/dist` on Vercel
- `loadEnv.ts` first in `app.ts`; CORS from `ALLOWED_ORIGINS`

New API: service ‚Üí controller ‚Üí route ‚Üí `app.ts` ‚Üí `docs/API.md`
